{{#> base_layout}}
<h2>Two-Factor Authentication Enabled</h2>
<p>Two-factor authentication has been successfully enabled on your account.</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Method:</strong> {{method}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0;"><strong>Enabled:</strong> {{time}}</p>
</div>

<p>Your account is now more secure. You'll be asked for a verification code in addition to your password when signing
    in.</p>

<div class="warning-box">
    <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Important:</strong> Make sure to save your backup codes in a safe place in case you
        lose access to your authenticator.</p>
</div>

<p class="muted">If you didn't enable two-factor authentication, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
{{/base_layout}}